msgctxt "84_Chatty Guy"
msgid "I hear the president of Sky Finance got hauled in by the\\r\n"\n"cops not too long ago."
msgstr "He oído que el presidente de Sky Finance ha sido arrestado\\r\n"\n"por la policía hace no mucho."

msgctxt "96_Chatty Guy"
msgid "Sounds like they let him off the hook right away, though.\\r\n"\n"Guess that means he didn't do anything wrong."
msgstr "Sin embargo parece que lo soltaron enseguida.\\r\n"\n"Supongo que eso significa que no hizo nada malo."

